channel.title: A really weird problem
channel.description:
Ok, I've been working on my NPC dialogue for my server. I had it working just fine literally 30min ago. I decided to move that NPC to another place. Now when I click on him it starts fishing lobbies? Ok that makes sense.
I moved him back where I put him in the first place and it still does it. I decided to try another NPC, but it does that for him too. It seems my dialogue only works for preexisting NPCS?
I have no idea what's up...
